вҚқ This Namespace includes tests for the function Membership which is represented by Dyadic Epsilon(вҲҠ)
вҚқ
вҚқ Membership (RвҶҗXвҲҠY)
вҚқ An element of X is considered identical to an element in Y if XвүЎY returns 1 for those elements.
:Namespace membership
    AssertвҶҗ#.unittest.Assert

    вҚқ Run Variations of each test with normal, empty and multiple shaped data
    вҲҮ tResвҶҗtData RunVariations exp ;actualR;actualRE;expectedR;left;right;res;tID;tCmt;lshape;lshapeW0;rshape;x;actualRM
        (expectedR left right)вҶҗexp
        (tID tCmt)вҶҗtData
        tResвҶҗвҚ¬

        вҚқ normal
        actualRвҶҗleftвҲҠright
        tRes,вҶҗtData Assert expectedRвүЎactualR

        вҚқ empty left
        actualREвҶҗ(0вҚҙleft)вҲҠright вҚқ 0 in the shape means we have no elements in the array, i.e. it's empty.
        tRes,вҶҗ('Empty',tID) tCmt Assert вҚ¬вүЎactualRE вҚқ empty array is expectedR

        вҚқ empty right
        actualREвҶҗleftвҲҠ(0вҚҙright) вҚқ 0 in the shape means we have no elements in the array, i.e. it's empty.
        tRes,вҶҗ('Empty',tID) tCmt Assert (0Г—expectedR)вүЎactualRE вҚқ all 0s in expectedR is the new expected result

        вҚқ different shapes
        вҚқ for ANY array lshape, and for any rightshape where (вүўright)вүӨГ—/rshape
        вҚқ the condition guarantees that (rshapeвҚҙright) will create an array
        вҚқ which contains ALL the elements of right, possibly more than once
        lshapeвҶҗ?4/4
        вҚқ randomized shape which has вүӨ4 elements and each elements is вүӨ12 and satisfies above condition
        rshapeвҶҗ{(Г—/(xвҶҗ(?4)?вҚӨ/?12))>вүўright:x вӢ„ вҲҮвҚө}вҚ¬
        actualRMвҶҗ(lshapeвҚҙleft)вҲҠ(rshapeвҚҙright)
        tRes,вҶҗ('Shape',tID) tCmt Assert (lshapeвҚҙexpectedR) вүЎ actualRM

        вҚқ different shapes with 0 in shape
        lshapeW0вҶҗ(0@(?4))lshape
        actualRMвҶҗ(lshapeW0вҚҙleft)вҲҠ(rshapeвҚҙright)
        tRes,вҶҗ('ShapeW0',tID) tCmt Assert (lshapeW0вҚҙ0) вүЎ actualRM
    вҲҮ

    вҚқ Read more about DR: https://help.dyalog.com/latest/#Language/System%20Functions/Data%20Representation%20Monadic.htm
    вҚқ Read more about CT and DCT: https://help.dyalog.com/latest/#Language/System%20Functions/ct.htm
    вҲҮ rвҶҗtest_membership ;w;n;r;data;case;data2;case2;type;bool;i1;char1;char2;i2;char3;i3;ptr;dbl;fl;cmplx;Hdbl;Hfl;Hcmplx;d;ct;fr;вҺ•CT;вҺ•DCT;вҺ•FR;ct_default;dct_default;fr_dbl;fr_decf;testDesc;desc
        ct_defaultвҶҗ1EВҜ14
        dct_defaultвҶҗ1EВҜ28
        fr_dblвҶҗ645
        fr_decfвҶҗ1287
        
        boolвҶҗ0 1                                      вҚқ 11: 1 bit Boolean type arrays
        i1вҶҗВҜ60+вҚі120                                   вҚқ 83: 8 bits signed integer
        char1вҶҗвҺ•UCS вҚі255                               вҚқ 80: 8 bits character
        char2вҶҗвҺ•UCS (1000+вҚі100)                        вҚқ 160: 16 bits character
        i2вҶҗ{вҚө,-вҚө}10000+вҚі100                           вҚқ 163: 16 bits signed integer
        char3вҶҗвҺ•UCS (100000+вҚі100)                      вҚқ 320: 32 bits character
        i3вҶҗ{вҚө,-вҚө}100000+вҚі100                          вҚқ 323: 32 bits signed integer
        ptrвҶҗ2,/вҺ•A                                     вҚқ 326: Pointer (32-bit or 64-bit as appropriate)
        dblвҶҗ{вҚө,-вҚө}i3+0.1                              вҚқ 645: 64 bits Floating
        cmplxвҶҗ{вҚө,-вҚө}(0J1Г—вҚі100)+вҢҪвҚі100                  вҚқ 1289: 128 bits Complex
        HcmplxвҶҗ{вҚө,-вҚө}(1E14J1E14Г—вҚі20)                  вҚқ 1289 but larger numbers to test for CT value
        вҚқ Hdbl is 645 but larger numbers to test for CT value
        вҚқ intervals of 2 are chosen because CT for these numbers +1 and -1
        вҚқ come under the region of tolerant equality
        HdblвҶҗ{вҚө,-вҚө}1E14+(2Г—вҚі50)
        вҚқ Hfl is 1287 but larger numbers to test for CT value
        вҚқ far intervals are chosen for non overlap 
        вҚқ with region of tolerant equality
        вҺ•FRвҶҗfr_decf
        flвҶҗ{вҚө,-вҚө}i3+0.01                              вҚқ 1287: 128 bits Decimal
        HflвҶҗ{вҚө,-вҚө}2E29+(1E16Г—вҚі10)
        вҺ•FRвҶҗfr_dbl

        rвҶҗвҚ¬
        testDescвҶҗ{'for ',case,{0вҲҠвҚҙcase2:'',вҚөвӢ„' , ', case2,вҚө},' & вҺ•CT вҺ•DCT:',вҺ•CT,вҺ•DCT, '& вҺ•FR:', вҺ•FR}

        :For ct :In 1 0 
            (вҺ•CT вҺ•DCT)вҶҗct Г— ct_default dct_default вҚқ set comparison tolerance

            :For fr :In 1 2
                вҺ•FRвҶҗfrвҠғfr_dbl fr_decf

                :For case :In 'i1' 'i2' 'i3' 'char1' 'char2' 'char3' 'ptr' 'dbl' 'fl' 'cmplx' 'Hdbl' 'Hfl' 'Hcmplx'
                    dataвҶҗвҚҺcase
                    :If вҺ•FR=fr_decf вҲ§ 1289=вҺ•DR data вҚқ вҺ•FR=1287 is not recommended to be used with cmplx
                        :Continue
                    :EndIf

                    вҚқ Cross type tests
                    :For case2 :In 'i1' 'i2' 'i3' 'char1' 'char2' 'char3' 'ptr' 'dbl' 'fl' 'cmplx' 'Hdbl' 'Hfl' 'Hcmplx'
                        data2вҶҗвҚҺcase2
                        descвҶҗtestDescвҚ¬
                        :If (dataвүЎdata2)
                            r,вҶҗ'TCross0' desc RunVariations (1вҚЁВЁdata) data data2
                            :Continue
                        :EndIf
                        r,вҶҗ 'TCross1' desc RunVariations (0вҚЁВЁdata) data data2                     вҚқ no match, all return 0
                        r,вҶҗ 'TCross2' desc RunVariations (0вҚЁВЁdata2) data2 data                    вҚқ no match, all return 0
                        r,вҶҗ 'TCross3' desc RunVariations (1вҚЁВЁdata) data (data,data2)              вҚқ first data match, returns 1
                        r,вҶҗ 'TCross4' desc RunVariations ((1вҚЁВЁdata),(0вҚЁВЁdata2)) (data,data2) data вҚқ data match, data2 no match
                    :EndFor
                    case2вҶҗвҚ¬ вҚқ disposing case2 for testDesc
                    descвҶҗtestDescвҚ¬

                    вҚқ same type tests
                    r,вҶҗ 'T1' desc RunVariations 1 (data[?вүўdata]) data           вҚқ random element is found
                    r,вҶҗ 'T2' desc RunVariations ((0вҚЁВЁВҜ1вҶ“data),1) data (ВҜ1вҶ‘data) вҚқ All elements return 0 except last
                    r,вҶҗ 'T3' desc RunVariations (1вҚЁВЁdata) data data             вҚқ all elements return 1
                    r,вҶҗ 'T4' desc RunVariations 0 5E50 data                     вҚқ huge element outside set is not found

                    вҚқ tests with comparison tolerance
                    dвҶҗdata[?вүўdata]
                    :If ct вҚқ tolerant
                        :If (вҠӮdata)вҲҠHdbl Hfl Hcmplx
                            вҚқ Hdbl=Hdbl+1 with default CT, but not for DECF
                            r,вҶҗ 'CTDefault' desc Assert ((1вүЎ(dвҲҠd+1)) вҲЁ (fr=2 вҲ§ caseвүЎ'Hdbl'))
                        :EndIf
                    :Else  вҚқ exact
                        :If ~(вҺ•DR data) вҲҠ 80 160 320 326 вҚқ non-numeric are skipped
                            вҚқ dвү d+1 for all numeric types, except when Hfl represented as DOUB
                            r,вҶҗ 'CTZero' desc Assert ((0вүЎ(dвҲҠd+1)) вҲЁ (fr=1 вҲ§ caseвүЎ'Hfl'))
                        :EndIf
                    :EndIf
                :EndFor

                вҚқ Booleans need special tests
                caseвҶҗ'bool'
                descвҶҗtestDescвҚ¬

                r,вҶҗ 'TB1' desc RunVariations 1 0 0
                r,вҶҗ 'TB2' desc RunVariations 1 (~0) 1
                r,вҶҗ 'TB3' desc RunVariations (1 1) bool bool

                вҚқ Boolean cross type tests
                :For case2 :In 'i1' 'i2' 'i3' 'char1' 'char2' 'char3' 'ptr' 'dbl' 'fl' 'cmplx'  'Hdbl' 'Hfl' 'Hcmplx'
                    data2вҶҗвҚҺcase2
                    descвҶҗtestDescвҚ¬
                    :If (83вү typeвҶҗвҺ•DR data2) вҚқ bool requires separate cross tests because of overlap with i1
                        r,вҶҗ 'TCrossBool1' desc RunVariations (0вҚЁВЁbool) bool data2  вҚқ All elements return 0
                        r,вҶҗ 'TCrossBool2' desc RunVariations (0вҚЁВЁdata2) data2 bool вҚқ All elements return 0
                    :Else
                        r,вҶҗ 'TCrossBooli1' desc RunVariations (1вҚЁВЁbool) bool data2 вҚқ All elements return 1
                        r,вҶҗ 'TCrossBooli2' desc RunVariations ({вҚө,(вҢҪвҚө)}((1вҶ“((вүўi1)Г·2)вҚҙ0),1)) data2 bool вҚқ overlaping 0 1 returns 1
                    :EndIf
                :EndFor
                case2вҶҗвҚ¬
            :EndFor
        :EndFor

    вҲҮ
:EndNamespace
